<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Students represent each number with objects and compare the objects to identify which number is less.</li>
      <li>Students draw a picture for each number to identify which number is less.</li>
      <li>Students identify the number that is less using the count sequence.</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


